|sat_logo|

.. |sat_logo| image:: ../images/logo_sat.png

:Author: Sylvain Cormier


Purpose
-------

Scripts to run test cases via telnet to satify system tests between two machines.

Files
+++++

start_miville.sh
dist_telnet_sys_test1.py
dist_telnet_sys_test2.py

Instructions
------------

Mofify line 41 of systest_telnet.py to fit IP address on each machine

::

	client_command = 'telnet IP address %s' % server_port


Run the start_miville.sh on each machine

::

	user@machine:~/src/miville/trunk/py/test/$sh miville.sh


Mofify line 41 of each dist_telnet_sys_test*.py to fit user and IP address on each machine.

::
	self.tst("contacts --add user IP address", "Contact added")

Run the scripts on each machine, starting with the receiver.

::

	user@machine:~/src/miville/trunk/py/$trial test/dist_telnet_sys_test1.py













